  "title": "EEG data for paper titled - Precise cortical contributions to feedback sensorimotor control during reactive balance",
  "description": "This dataset contains electroencephalography (EEG) recordings collected to investigate the cortical mechanisms underlying sensorimotor feedback control during reactive balance tasks. The data support a study examining precise cortical contributions to balance control in response to perturbations, providing insights into the neural basis of postural stability and reactive motor responses.",
